-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/ford-chief-will-miss-geneva-car-show-to-attend-cebit-ft-says.html
  Alan Mulally ,  Ford Motor Co .’s chief
executive officer, will miss next week’s Geneva auto show in
order to attend the digital industry’s CeBIT show in Hanover,  Germany , the Financial Times reported, citing a company
sportsman.  To contact the reporter on this story:
